metadata.name: Frankie Styles - PRIME
metadata.description:
This is will the First Single in not only 2023 but of my Upcoming Album Fragments due to release sometime in 2023. 

This song was made when i needed to find a new way about living life after moving to LA to pursue music. I needed something that felt larger than life and out came this song. It is called Prime as it feels like I am allowing my primal self to be released into the world. Thank you and Enjoy the music 

-Frankie Styles <3
